ATTENDANCE REQUIREMENT
--------------------------------
- Keep SeenUsers validation for attendee-only interactions.
- Remove or revise it only when off-roster targets should be allowed.

VARIABLE NAME
--------------------------------
- Leave HugStats unchanged for the stats, leaderboard, and reset actions.

PHRASES / RESPONSES
--------------------------------
